      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's been about 20 mins and it's still leaking a bit, but not like a lot. i just dont want to pay for a doctor visit or deal with the hospital if i can avoid it. do you think the honey is actually strong enough to do the job instead of needing stitches? i read online that honey is basically as good as some antibiotics.",
